name: 👺 TIGER CLAN MASK
description:
A unique opportunity has arisen for a new clan leader...

The owner of this clan mask will become leader of the clan, which will bestow the holder with unique benefits as the story unfolds.

To gain possession of the clan mask, you must:
- place a qualifying bid via objkt.com
- not currently hold a clan leader title

A qualifying bid must be:
- made on the objkt.com website via the offer button
- 18xtz
- made by a holder of a samurai of the same clan (one mask/clan per person only).

Bids will be checked for ownership and the first qualifying bid will be accepted and the winner will receive the clan leader title...

GOOD LUCK 

👺
